											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="The player reaches their arm out, palm outstretched, over the ritual circle. The infernal marble is in it. It begins to glow, and the entire room around it darkens. As the player closes their fist around the infernal marble, we see them from above, and the the blood underneath the player's closed fist lights ablaze, tracing around the ritual circle's outline in fire. The player drops the infernal marble, and the floor within the blazing outline ripples, We are no longer seeing a wooden floor, we see the crackling sky of Avernus." />
										</node>
